1
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:12,450
Dengar baik-baik, semuanya!

2
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:15,410
Orang yang duduk di belakangku ini ...

3
00:00:15,730 --> 00:00:17,610
... adalah kapten divisi ketiga yang baru,

4
00:00:17,760 --> 00:00:19,520
Kisaki Tetta!

5
00:00:25,620 --> 00:00:27,420
Walah, ada apaan, nih?

6
00:00:28,720 --> 00:00:30,830
Situasinya jadi semakin seru, nih.

7
00:00:36,780 --> 00:00:38,440
Untuk apa kau kemari, Baji?

8
00:00:38,510 --> 00:00:41,800
Harusnya kau dilarang mengikuti rapat kami
karena memicu perseteruan internal.

9
00:00:41,900 --> 00:00:45,760
Aku yang sudah
mengacaukan rapat pentingmu,

10
00:00:45,990 --> 00:00:47,770
apakah kali ini bakal dipecat?

11
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:51,340
Apaan?
Dia bicara apaan?

12
00:00:52,470 --> 00:00:55,530
Mikey, kau tidak butuh
pembuat onar, 'kan?

13
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:57,200
Baji!

14
00:00:58,950 --> 00:01:00,390
Aku akan keluar dari Touman.

15
00:01:01,100 --> 00:01:04,580
Kapten divisi pertama, Baji Keisuke,

16
00:01:04,959 --> 00:01:07,720
mulai hari ini akan
menjadi musuh Touman.

17
00:01:11,210 --> 00:01:13,539
Aku punya permintaan, Takemicchi.

18
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:16,080
Iya.

19
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:19,010
Bawalah Baji kembali dari Valhalla.

20
00:01:19,820 --> 00:01:21,600
Bolehkah aku minta
tolong hal itu padamu?

21
00:01:22,710 --> 00:01:23,490
Baik!

22
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:25,850
Boleh saja kalau itu permintaanmu!

23
00:01:26,450 --> 00:01:27,500
Tapi,

24
00:01:27,940 --> 00:01:31,570
apa aku juga boleh minta
tolong satu hal saja?

25
00:01:33,220 --> 00:01:34,490
Kisaki ....

26
00:01:35,289 --> 00:01:37,360
Tolong singkirkan Kisaki dari Touman.

27
00:01:38,100 --> 00:01:39,030
Boleh saja.

28
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:42,470
Dalam waktu dekat,
kita akan bentrok dengan Valhalla.

29
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:45,700
Sebelum itu terjadi, kau harus
membawa Baji kembali.

30
00:01:46,020 --> 00:01:49,440
Buktikanlah bahwa kau lebih
berguna dibanding Kisaki.

31
00:02:15,340 --> 00:02:19,010
(SMP Mizo)

32
00:02:35,220 --> 00:02:36,630
Hei, jangan berlarian di koridor.

33
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:53,570
Bawalah Baji kembali dari Valhalla.

34
00:02:53,970 --> 00:02:55,210
Kalau kau gagal,

35
00:02:56,070 --> 00:02:56,980
akan kubunuh!

36
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,070
'Gimana, nih?

37
00:03:00,480 --> 00:03:01,630
Takemichi.

38
00:03:01,700 --> 00:03:02,800
Ah?

39
00:03:02,940 --> 00:03:06,970
Aku sudah dengar, loh.
Katanya kau jadi anggota Touman.

40
00:03:07,220 --> 00:03:08,400
Akkun.

41
00:03:12,370 --> 00:03:12,820
Eh?

42
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:15,240
Ada apa?
Kok mukamu murung begitu?

43
00:03:15,730 --> 00:03:16,370
Eh?

44
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:17,150
Ah.

45
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,340
Benarkah?

46
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:21,270
Aku jadi anggota Touman, nih.

47
00:03:21,410 --> 00:03:22,430
Mengalir begitu saja.

48
00:03:22,970 --> 00:03:23,760
Wih.

49
00:03:23,760 --> 00:03:25,130
Apa yang terjadi?

50
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:28,590
Aku enggak bisa menatap
langsung ke wajah Akkun!

51
00:03:29,340 --> 00:03:31,970
Si cengeng Takemichi
bergabung dengan Touman?

52
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,400
Kami juga mau masuk.

53
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:36,260
Soal itu ....

54
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,860
Itu bukanlah hal bagus
seperti yang kalian kira.

55
00:03:39,250 --> 00:03:40,210
Hah?

56
00:03:40,660 --> 00:03:42,210
Eh?

57
00:03:44,220 --> 00:03:48,870
Kerah kami ditarik, dan diberi bogem mentah

58
00:03:49,130 --> 00:03:53,730
sehingga kami sempoyongan,
lalu jongkok bersebelahan

59
00:03:53,770 --> 00:03:58,560
Di tengah hujan yang diprediksi,
kau menyeringai

60
00:03:58,820 --> 00:04:04,400
lalu berbohong bahwa "luka pasti akan sembuh"

61
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:07,420
Bahkan adu mulut yang sering dilakukan

62
00:04:08,090 --> 00:04:12,660
tak bisa kulakukan dengan baik

63
00:04:12,820 --> 00:04:17,720
Jangan katakan candaan
yang membosankan

64
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:22,970
Rasa bosannya pun tampak jelas di mataku!

65
00:04:23,030 --> 00:04:30,670
Tak peduli walau seberapa banyak air
mata yang mengaliri pipi lebamku ini

66
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:37,340
melalui hati yang goyah
bersanding dengan bahu

67
00:04:37,409 --> 00:04:41,900
kau pasti bisa menghindari
akhir buruk yang menghantui!

68
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:47,470
Kenapa rasa sakit ini lebih
nyaman dibanding kebahagiaan?

69
00:04:47,580 --> 00:04:51,840
Bahkan rasa sakit ini kian menggema!

70
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:56,480
Sambil menggigit lidah dan
mengenakan baju basah,

71
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:59,690
mari kita tertawakan wajah sembap ini

72
00:05:00,060 --> 00:05:04,430
Lalu di tengah malam bermandikan hujan

73
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:12,200
kita ikrarkan balas dendam!

74
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:20,920
(#15 Tanpa Pengorbanan, Tiada Kemenangan)

75
00:05:16,100 --> 00:05:17,770
Rupanya begitu.

76
00:05:18,060 --> 00:05:23,220
Kalau kau tidak bisa memulangkan mantan kapten
divisi pertama yang bernama Baji dari Valhalla,

77
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:25,880
kau akan dibunuh Mikey, ya.

78
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:26,820
Iya.

79
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:30,480
Terlebih, batas waktunya cuma
sampai Touman bentrok dengan Valhalla.

80
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:33,250
Bukannya kita enggak tahu
kapan mereka akan bentrok?

81
00:05:33,430 --> 00:05:34,590
'Gimana kalau hari ini?

82
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,640
Beristirahatlah dengan tenang, Takemichi.

83
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:38,190
Aku akan memungut tulangmu.

84
00:05:38,620 --> 00:05:43,260
Tapi, sejujurnya aku enggak tahu
bagaimana kondisi internalnya Touman.

85
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:46,320
Aku juga enggak tahu levelnya
Valhalla itu sejauh apa.

86
00:05:46,620 --> 00:05:48,390
Oi, ensiklopedia berandalan.

87
00:05:48,580 --> 00:05:49,270
Hah?

88
00:05:49,390 --> 00:05:51,330
Apa boleh buat, ya.

89
00:05:51,340 --> 00:05:53,190
Aku akan menjelaskannya.

90
00:05:55,780 --> 00:05:57,360
Geng Tokyo Manji.

91
00:05:57,460 --> 00:05:59,000
Disingkatnya Touman.

92
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,600
Ketuanya adalah Bang Mikey,

93
00:06:00,620 --> 00:06:02,560
dan wakil ketuanya
bernama Bang Draken.

94
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:04,430
Di bawahnya terdapat 5 divisi.

95
00:06:04,510 --> 00:06:07,560
Setiap divisinya berisi sekitar 20 anggota.

96
00:06:07,420 --> 00:06:13,470
(Geng Tokyo Manji) (Ketua Mikey - Wakil Draken)
(Div: Pertama - Kedua - Ketiga - Keempat - Kelima)

97
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:10,550
Geng motor besar yang jumlah
anggotanya sekitar 100.

98
00:06:11,340 --> 00:06:13,670
Sejauh ini, kau sudah tahu, 'kan?

99
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:14,690
Wih.

100
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:15,810
Aku baru tahu.

101
00:06:15,900 --> 00:06:17,410
Eh? Seriusan?

102
00:06:17,450 --> 00:06:19,360
Bukannya kau berandalan?!

103
00:06:19,420 --> 00:06:20,270
Maaf.

104
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:21,780
Dicatat, ya.

105
00:06:21,810 --> 00:06:23,550
Ini bakal muncul di ujian.

106
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:24,920
Ah.

107
00:06:24,950 --> 00:06:26,390
Yang di situ, jangan tertawa!

108
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:28,070
Dia malah terbawa suasana.

109
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,570
Dari apa yang kudengar,

110
00:06:31,620 --> 00:06:35,000
mantan ketua divisi ketiga yang
bernama Bang Pachin ditangkap,

111
00:06:35,100 --> 00:06:38,860
dan wakil ketua yang bernama Bang Pehyan
masuk ke dalam divisi kedua.

112
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:39,650
Eh?

113
00:06:39,700 --> 00:06:43,030
Berarti, Bang Pehyan menjadi
bawahan Bang Mitsuya?

114
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:43,860
Iya.

115
00:06:44,250 --> 00:06:46,110
Satu divisi, toh?

116
00:06:46,180 --> 00:06:48,640
Aku enggak akrab sama Bang Pehyan.

117
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,790
Takemicchi!

118
00:06:49,820 --> 00:06:50,960
Suaranya seram.

119
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:55,060
(Geng Tokyo Manji)
(Ketua Mikey - Wakil Draken)

120
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:55,060
Terus, orang yang menjadi
kapten baru divisi ketiga adalah ....

121
00:06:56,340 --> 00:06:57,280
Kisaki.

122
00:06:57,800 --> 00:07:00,270
Benar. Mantan anggota Moebius.

123
00:07:00,420 --> 00:07:04,000
Moebius juga bukan satu kesatuan.

124
00:07:04,060 --> 00:07:07,100
Karena kabarnya, grup Osanai
yang lahir pada tahun 1988,

125
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:09,610
dan grup Kisaki yang
lahir pada tahun 1990,

126
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:11,350
sedang berselisih.

127
00:07:11,540 --> 00:07:13,370
Oalah begitu.

128
00:07:13,420 --> 00:07:15,800
Meski satu tim, tapi banyak masalahnya, ya.

129
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:18,040
Lalu, Osanai kalah sama Mikey.

130
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:20,370
Kemudian, Moebius pun bubar.

131
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:24,580
Terus, grup tahun 1990 yang dipimpin
Kisaki pun bergabung dengan Touman.

132
00:07:24,620 --> 00:07:29,050
Lalu, anggota Touman pun melonjak
dari 100 menjadi 150 anggota.

133
00:07:29,420 --> 00:07:35,040
(Divisi Kedua - Divisi Ketiga - Divisi Keempat)

134
00:07:29,420 --> 00:07:30,750
Di Touman,

135
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:35,040
divisi ketiga yang dipimpin oleh
Kisaki menjadi divisi terbesar.

136
00:07:35,659 --> 00:07:37,370
Bagi Touman ke depannya,

137
00:07:37,650 --> 00:07:39,630
kekuatan Kisaki diperlukan.

138
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:45,760
Lalu bagaimana dengan anggota
kelahiran 1988 yang dipimpin Osanai?

139
00:07:46,820 --> 00:07:50,500
Yang menyatukan sisa
anggota kelahiran 1988-1989 adalah ....

140
00:07:50,740 --> 00:07:52,060
Hanma Shuji.

141
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:54,500
Dia?

142
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:56,600
Ah.

143
00:07:57,220 --> 00:07:58,159
Benar juga.

144
00:07:58,220 --> 00:08:02,310
Sewaktu tawuran 3 Agustus, dia berkata
kalau dirinya adalah ketua sementara Moebius.

145
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:04,480
Kemudian, si Hanma ini,

146
00:08:04,540 --> 00:08:08,290
yang menyatukan Moebius
dan fraksi anti Touman,

147
00:08:08,400 --> 00:08:09,700
lalu membentuk Valhalla.

148
00:08:10,190 --> 00:08:12,930
Saat ini, jumlah anggota
Valhalla sebanyak 300!

149
00:08:13,340 --> 00:08:15,010
300?

150
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:18,140
Terlebih, Hanma menjadi pemimpin Valhalla?

151
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:19,850
Cih, cih, cih.

152
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:22,500
Hanma itu ketua pengganti.

153
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:25,030
Tidak ada yang tahu
siapa ketua sebenarnya.

154
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:27,370
Ketuanya tidak berwajah.

155
00:08:27,570 --> 00:08:28,970
Makanya, Valhalla dijuluki

156
00:08:29,130 --> 00:08:32,640
sebagai malaikat tanpa kepala.

157
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:35,669
Bang Baji berada di tim seperti itu?

158
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:38,250
Untuk bisa membawa Bang
Baji kembali ke Touman,

159
00:08:38,580 --> 00:08:41,440
kayaknya aku harus menemuinya.

160
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:43,980
Tapi, 'gimana caranya?

161
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:46,180
Sip.

162
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,390
Hei, hei.

163
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:48,000
Ah?

164
00:08:48,090 --> 00:08:50,640
Apa kalian tahu kelasnya Hanagaki,
murid tahun kedua?

165
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:52,760
Eh? Kelas 2-3.

166
00:08:53,050 --> 00:08:54,210
Oh.

167
00:08:54,420 --> 00:08:55,580
Terima kasih.

168
00:09:00,500 --> 00:09:02,900
Memangnya di sekolah kita
ada cowok seganteng dia?

169
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:05,350
Dari warna sepatunya,
dia anak tahun ketiga, 'kan?

170
00:09:06,540 --> 00:09:10,100
Yang menyatukan mantan anggota Moebius
adalah si nomor dua Hanma.

171
00:09:10,490 --> 00:09:13,360
Lalu, yang menyatukan
fraksi anti Touman adalah ...

172
00:09:17,530 --> 00:09:20,200
... si nomor tiga, Hanemiya Kazutora.

173
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:22,050
Ah.

174
00:09:22,390 --> 00:09:23,010
Eh?

175
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:24,020
Oh?

176
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,150
Wah.

177
00:09:28,740 --> 00:09:29,760
Loh?

178
00:09:40,340 --> 00:09:43,200
Jangan-jangan, sekolah sudah beres?

179
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:46,630
Keparat, siapa kau?
Wajahmu belum pernah kulihat.

180
00:09:46,780 --> 00:09:48,850
Kok tiba-tiba kasar?

181
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:51,370
Begini-begini, aku senior kalian di SMP ini.

182
00:09:51,510 --> 00:09:52,110
Hah?

183
00:09:52,210 --> 00:09:54,360
Siapa kau?
Aku belum pernah melihatmu.

184
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:03,020
Tato harimau di lehernya!

185
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,820
Hentikan, Makoto!
Orang ini ....

186
00:10:04,830 --> 00:10:06,520
Hah? Apaan, sih?

187
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:08,130
Hei, hei.

188
00:10:08,210 --> 00:10:10,250
Apa kalian kenal Hanagaki Takemichi?

189
00:10:10,610 --> 00:10:10,990
Eh?

190
00:10:11,030 --> 00:10:13,500
Ta-Takemichi, keluarlah.

191
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:14,850
Hah?

192
00:10:15,630 --> 00:10:16,800
Takemichi?

193
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:20,800
O-Orang ini merupakan
si nomor tiga di Valhalla,

194
00:10:20,820 --> 00:10:22,870
Hanemiya Kazutora!

195
00:10:22,390 --> 00:10:25,220
(Valhalla No.3 - Hanemiya Kazutora)

196
00:10:25,340 --> 00:10:26,400
Eh?!

197
00:10:29,190 --> 00:10:30,460
Senangnya!

198
00:10:30,700 --> 00:10:33,780
Tidak kusangka ada adik kelasku
yang bergabung dengan Touman!

199
00:10:34,460 --> 00:10:35,640
Oke, Takemichi.

200
00:10:35,810 --> 00:10:36,140
Eh?

201
00:10:36,140 --> 00:10:37,770
Ayo kita ke markas Valhalla.

202
00:10:37,820 --> 00:10:39,380
Eh? Valhalla?

203
00:10:39,620 --> 00:10:42,310
Oi, Takemichi-nya ketemu, nih.

204
00:10:42,570 --> 00:10:43,130
Hah?

205
00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:44,890
Dia, ya?

206
00:10:44,980 --> 00:10:45,730
Oi.

207
00:10:45,940 --> 00:10:48,000
Me-Mereka siapa, ya?

208
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,170
Hah?

209
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:51,650
Junior yang paling kupercaya.

210
00:10:52,100 --> 00:10:52,530
Eh?

211
00:10:53,020 --> 00:10:53,970
Wih ....

212
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,850
Apa terjadi sesuatu pada mereka?

213
00:10:56,010 --> 00:10:57,440
Soalnya mereka memakai kruk.

214
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:58,500
Hah?

215
00:10:58,660 --> 00:10:59,850
Kemarin kupatahkan.

216
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:00,810
Eh?

217
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:03,810
Mereka orang yang paling
dipercaya olehmu, 'kan?

218
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:04,760
Iya.

219
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:07,060
Apa kau mau protes sama Bang Kazutora?

220
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,470
Enggak.

221
00:11:09,980 --> 00:11:14,360
Kenapa orang-orang ini bisa kalem
meski kakinya patah?

222
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:17,670
Terus, orang ini pasti berbahaya!

223
00:11:18,180 --> 00:11:20,230
Buruan, Takemichi.

224
00:11:20,340 --> 00:11:22,120
Nomor tiga di Valhalla.

225
00:11:22,190 --> 00:11:23,890
Hanemiya Kazutora.

226
00:11:24,140 --> 00:11:27,010
Bukannya bahaya kalau
aku mengikutnya?

227
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,800
Ke markasnya musuh, loh!

228
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:31,080
Jangan gugup.

229
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:32,910
Akan kupertemukan dengan mereka.

230
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:34,200
Mereka?

231
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:37,800
Jangan-jangan ini kesempatanku
bertemu Bang Baji?

232
00:11:38,850 --> 00:11:41,850
Tapi, aku agak takut.

233
00:11:43,490 --> 00:11:44,070
Uh!

234
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:53,540
Mau ke kedai yang kubahas tempo hari?

235
00:11:53,560 --> 00:11:54,770
Mau, mau!

236
00:11:54,870 --> 00:11:56,590
Hari ini enaknya makan apa, ya?

237
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:57,810
Hina.

238
00:11:57,920 --> 00:11:58,920
Mau makan parfe!

239
00:11:58,960 --> 00:11:59,740
